        "action": "Update guidance requiring schools to take kids' temperatures at school gates",
        "additional_details": "My son has an underlying health condition. This would help all children with underlying health conditions to feel safe in returning to school in this worrying time. It could also protect the staff work force too. So we would like this to be included in the guidelines so school have to take temperatures. The school don\u2019t see it as necessary due to government guidelines. We need this changed.",
        "background": "Make it mandatory for schools to be taking the children\u2019s temperature at the school gates during a pandemic",
